# Ops dashboard — static UI on the main Ekasi Pay API (ekasi-pay-api).

# Dev: Vite proxies /api → local API (default http://localhost:8787).
# Prod: API_HOST / VITE_API_URL set at build time.

# One ops login account is managed by the MAIN API env vars:
#   OPS_SUPER_ADMIN_USERNAME=superadmin   (login username)
#   OPS_DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=your-password  (login password)
# On each API start those values are synced into ops_admin_users.
#
# Also set FRONTEND_ORIGINS on ekasi-pay-api to include this ops site URL.
